%h1 Product Listing Page
%br
%hr

%h1 Your Products

- @products.each do |product|
  .well
    .row
      .col-md-3
        = image_tag product.images.first.image.url(:preview)
      .col-md-9
        %p= link_to product.name, product_path(product)
        %p= product.description.truncate(150)
        %p
          $
          = product.price
        %p
          - if product.sold_out?
            = "This product is currently sold out!"
.row
  %td.text-center{colspan: "6"}
    = will_paginate @products, search: @search_term, renderer: BootstrapPagination::Rails